text: == Events == * 15 March – Henry the Fowler defeats the Magyars in the Battle of Riade. * Cotentin and Jersey are taken by William I, Duke of Normandy. * The Kingdom of Lower Burgundy is given to King Rudolph II of Upper Burgundy. == Deaths == * King Alfonso IV of Leon * December 15 – Li Siyuan, Emperor Mingzong of Later Tang Category:930s
